              <h3>To maintain a healthy and respectful environment, all users must follow these guidelines:</h3>

              <ul>
                <li>Respect all users and mentors.</li>
                <li>Avoid sharing offensive, abusive, or harmful content.</li>
                <li>Do not misuse the anonymous chat feature.</li>
                <li>Follow academic integrity and honesty.</li>
                <li>Mentors should provide genuine and helpful guidance.</li>
                <li> Do not share personal contact details (phone number, address, etc.) publicly.</li>
                <li>Avoid spamming messages or sending repeated content.</li>
                <li>Do not share false or misleading information.</li>
                <li>Use the platform only for educational and guidance purposes.</li>
                <li> Maintain polite and professional communication.</li>
                <li>Do not impersonate another user or mentor.</li>
                <li>Report any inappropriate behavior to the admin.</li>
                <li>Do not upload or share copyrighted or illegal content.</li>
                <li>Respect privacy of other users at all times.</li>
                <li>Use appropriate language in chats and posts.</li>
              </ul>
             
        </div>

